      "amount": "1 teaspoon"
    },
    {
      "name": "Black Pepper",
      "amount": "1 teaspoon"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "In a small bowl, mix together palm sugar and nam tan pip until well combined.",
    "In a separate bowl, toss together onion, garlic, mushrooms, bell peppers, and potatoes with olive oil, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Spread the vegetables on a baking sheet and roast for 20 minutes.",
    "Remove the vegetables from the oven and brush with the palm sugar and nam tan pip mixture.",
    "Return the vegetables to the oven and continue roasting for an additional 15 minutes.",
    "Season with rosemary and serve hot."
  ],
